PrecisReappointment of MARIAN L. ROBSON, of Vancouver, British Columbia, as a member of the Canadian Transportation Agency to hold office during good behaviour for a term of five years; and designation of MARIAN L. ROBSON as Chairperson of the Canadian Transportation Agency, effective July 1, 2001.
